data.description: Welcome to this 4 bed 3.5 bath 2 story home w/ 2 car garage tucked in desirable Cross Keys Estates. You are welcomed into the front foyer w/ beautiful white spindled staircase. To the right is the formal living room or if it suits you better, an office/study. To the left is the formal dining room. Head back to towards the open style great room featuring gorgeous floor to ceiling brick surround fireplace, large bay window & breakfast room. Kitchen offers white cabinetry, large peninsula top w/ designer laminate counter tops, & hard wood floors. Head out to large deck overlooking the level fenced backyard. Perfect spot to entertain family & friends this spring. Main floor laundry. Master bedroom is a perfect escape w/ dual closets & vanities plus separate soaking tub & shower. Three more generously sized bedrooms & hall bath complete the upper level. Full finished basement offers large family room, full bath, separate room perfect for exercise room or office plus still room for storage!
